headline: JLL arranges $1.2B refinancing of iconic Dallas shopping destination
summary: JLL's Capital Markets Group announced today that it has arranged a $1.2 billion refinancing package for NorthPark Center, a Class A++ super-regional shopping center located in Dallas, Texas.
